      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ZINFANDEL PEARL (1) was on speed settling but found some traffic when checked, missing the frame to finish fourth (31.85) at this track in a Maiden. Better than latest and worth another try. SPEED RAIDER (4) showed ability on debut filling a minor placing when third (23.50) at Gawler over 400m. Meets a moderate line up and should do much better. ADHANA DEREK (2) is long overdue and boasts a solid record despite not having won his maiden yet, the latest finishing second at this track. Although beaten was on pace and game in defeat. Will give a great sight again. WILLOW TYSON (7) will run well despite no experience on this trip.",
